rut" style=3D"height: 0.6944em;"></span><span class=3D"mord mathnormal" sty=
le=3D"margin-right: 0.0315em;">k</span></span></span></span></span> events =
over a time period for any non-negative integer value of <span><span class=
=3D"katex"><span class=3D"katex-mathml"><math xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/19=
98/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>k</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=3D"a=
pplication/x-tex">k</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=3D"ka=
tex-html" aria-hidden=3D"true"><span class=3D"base"><span class=3D"strut" s=
tyle=3D"height: 0.6944em;"></span><span class=3D"mord mathnormal" style=3D"=
margin-right: 0.0315em;">k</span></span></span></span></span>.</p>

<blockquote class=3D"features"><p>
Let <span><span class=3D"katex"><span class=3D"katex-mathml"><math xmlns=3D=
"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>X</mi></mrow><ann=
otation encoding=3D"application/x-tex">X</annotation></semantics></math></s=
