></span></span>  The goal of this problem is to find <span><span class=3D"k=
atex"><span class=3D"katex-mathml"><math xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Ma=
th/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>P</mi><mo stretchy=3D"false">(</mo><mi>X</m=
