/span> independent trials, <span><span class=3D"katex"><span class=3D"katex=
-mathml"><math xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mro=
w><mi>p</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=3D"application/x-tex">p</annotation=
></semantics></math></span><span class=3D"katex-html" aria-hidden=3D"true">=
